sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.services

Interface Manager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Nameable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DebugListenerManager, DebugManager, DebugResourceManager, ListenerManager, ResourceManager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractListenerManager, AbstractManager, AbstractResourceManager, DebugListenerManagerProxy, DebugResourceManagerProxy, ForwardingListenerManager, ForwardingManager, ForwardingResourceManager

    public interface Manager
extends Nameable
    An object managing other objects, usually Registrable instances.

    Uniqueness of a manager is determined by its qualified name. Two Manager instances with the same qualified name should be implemented by the same class, provide the same functionality and behave the same way.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
